! This is a lexicon to be used with aspell spell checker only.
! Target is to use as many sublexicons as possible with as many variables
! as possible to create aspell affix file.
LEXICON AspellAffix

!BISYLLABIC
! GOAHTI lexicon has consonant gradation and dipthtong simplification
! Cases: -i, -á, -u, -a, -e, and -o endings
! Obsolete because GOAHTI has same endings as GADDI ??
!buohkki GOAHTI ;
!buohkká GOAHTI ;
!duohkku GOAHTI ;
!fuohkka GOAHTI ;
!fuohkke GOAHTI ;
!buohkko GOAHTI ;
! GADDI lexicon has comparative forms
! Cases: -i, -á, -u, -a, -e, and -o endings
buohkki GADDI ;
cuohkká GADDI ;
duohkku GADDI ;
fuohkka GADDI ;
guohkke GADDI ;
huohkko GADDI ;
! IIJA non-gradating w/ a-ill
guohkkinymiija IIJA ; ! other case endings?
! STAHTA non-gradating w/ a/i-ill/
buohkkistáhta STAHTA ;

!TRISYLLABIC
! SEAMU gradating trisyllabic
! Cases: -i, -a, and -u endings
jea0lu:jeallum8 SEAMU ;
kuo0mi:kuopmán8 SEAMU ;
muo0mu:muopmum8 SEAMU ;
nea0na:neatnag8 SEAMU ;
! MALIS gradating w/ consonant endings
! Cases: -is, -uš, and -ir endings
buoh0pis:buoh'pis MALIS ;
duoh0puš:duoh'puš MALIS ;
goah0pir:goah'pir MALIS ;
! Cases: -is, -uš, and -ir endings

!CONTRACTED
! SUOLU contracted
! Cases: -u ending only?
suo00zu:suohccu SUOLU ;
! FALIS contracted
! Cases: -is only?
fálggis:fál'gis FALIS ;

!MISC
! LEXDIMINC diminutives
beanáš:beanáž LEXDIMINC ;

! Add more and correct these.

!LEXICON NOUNONLYAFTERNUMBER
!čiegahas:čiegahass JOHTOLAT ;

!LEXICON NOUNALSOAFTERNUMBER
!# ;

! bahá: Seamma subst ferte lea guokte geardde. Čiegahas ii gávdno okto.
! molssueaktu: Vqldit miellahtutut eret NounRoot:as, ja geavahit 121.

LEXICON NounRoot

!NOUNALSOAFTERNUMBER ; ! Pointing to a subclass of nouns which frequently may,
         ! but must not, occur after a numeral:


!^GUESSNOUNROOT GuessNoun ; !^C^
! AGNoun ;

! Stray forms, with defect paradigms
sadji+N+Sg+Gen:saje%> K ; ! Normal is saji, this is hard-coded.
hávvi+N+Sg+Gen:háve%> K ; ! Same here.
áigi+N+Sg+Gen:áigge%> K ; ! And here.
geassi+N+Sg+Gen:gease%> K ; ! Adverbial form, like those above.

eise#váldi+N+Pl+Gen:eiseváldiid9 K ; !SUB Wrong, but 18x in corp.
eise#váldi+N+Pl+Acc:eiseváldiid9 K ; !SUB
eise#váldi+N+Pl+Nom:eiseváldit K ; !SUB Wrong, but 97x in corp.
mátki+N+Pl+Gen:mátkiid K ; !SUB Wrong.
vánhen+N+Pl+Nom:vánhemmat K ; !SUB Wrong, probably dialectal form.
